summary:
Data:
In an era where data is omnipresent and growing at an unprecedented rate, I believe it's those who can harness its power who will truly shape the future. I'm excited to leverage my skills and passion to contribute to this data-driven revolution."

Myself:
Masters graduate in Marketing Analytics & Data Science, brimming with an unquenchable thirst for knowledge and a solid foundation in key technical skills. I bring a strong understanding of data analysis techniques, proficiency in R and SQL, and a dedication to learning and applying cutting-edge practices in the field. My experiences during my degree, coupled with my love for problem-solving, have equipped me to frame and tackle data challenges in innovative ways.
